{"_path":"/gists/neuroscience","_dir":"gists","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"神经科学","description":"神经科学也即脑科学，是一门以脑结构和功能为研究对象的综合学科，横跨了多个学科领域。现代神经科学有三个主流分支：细胞和分子神经科学、认知神经科学和发育神经学。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"神经科学"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"神经科学"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"神经科学也即脑科学，是一门以脑结构和功能为研究对象的综合学科，横跨了多个学科领域。现代神经科学有三个主流分支：细胞和分子神经科学、认知神经科学和发育神经学。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"时间线"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"时间线"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"象形字“脑”","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20211208004256.png?w=30"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"古埃及人的象形字作品《史密斯外科纸草书》（约 B.C. 3000 ~ B.C. 1700）中第一次出现了文字“脑”，并记录一些相关的有趣的案例。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希波克拉底（约 B.C. 500）认为脑是精神的载体，“人们应当认识到：我们的愉悦、欢乐、笑声和谈谐都来自脑，而且仅仅来自脑；还有我们的忧愁、痛苦及爱恋和哭泣。”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与希波克拉底相反，亚里士多德（B.C. 384 ~ B.C. 322）认为精神在心。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"加仑（B.C. 129 ~ D.C. 199）支持精神在脑，并且通过实验证明了发音受喉返神经控制。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"达芬奇（1452~1519）在人体解剖学有所建树，他绘制了拥有四个脑室的脑图，并制作了牛脑室的灌注蜡模。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"维萨里（1514~1564）通过解剖，基本完善了今日神经科学教科书上关于脑的描述。著有《人体构造》（1543）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"笛卡尔（1596~1650）认为脑只是和其它器官别无两样的器官，可以比拟为机械运动而加以描述和研究，因此开创了脑功能的分析和实验研究。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"威利斯（1621~1675）在《大脑解剖》（1664）中广泛讨论了脑的生理、解剖、化学、临床神经学。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"18 世纪末，伽伐尼发现动物电：蛙腿可因神经接受电刺激而收缩，神经肌肉活动时有电产生。神经活动的实质是生物电活动，这种观念一句扫除了过去把精神归结为灵魂、元气、精灵或微小颗粒的活动等旧观念。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1839 年施莱登和施旺提出细胞理论，拉蒙-卡哈尔在此基础上提出神经元学说，认为细胞理论同样适用于神经细胞。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1887 年，弗里乔夫·南森认为智力存在于脑中大量的神经细胞连接之中。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1897 年，谢灵顿提出突触理论，后提出神经系统整合作用理论：中枢神经系统接受神经传入形成输出主要靠抑制作用，并在 1932 年受诺贝尔奖。突触理论在 1950 年代电子显微镜出现后得到了实验证实。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"19 世纪末，加尔提出颅相学，最早认为大脑各区具有功能上的特异性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1950 年代，里奥克成立第一个神经科学实验室。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1968 年，米勒、杰拉尔德和芒卡斯尔创办了第一次神经科学学会会议，与会 600 人。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1978 年，考恩出版《神经科学年鉴》。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"相关文献"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相关文献"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"大脑帝国"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/_books/9787508692876"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《大脑帝国》"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"名词译注"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"名词译注"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中译"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"英文"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"精神"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"mind"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"阅读更多"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"阅读更多"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://xueshu.baidu.com/usercenter/paper/show?paperid=13cd1e266dc30588916159be12586884&site=xueshu_se","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《神经科学的发展历史》"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/20420048","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《艾德温·史密斯（外科）纸草文稿》"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1664289015456647938","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《颅相学：一门伪科学的兴衰史》"}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"时间线","depth":2,"text":"时间线"},{"id":"相关文献","depth":2,"text":"相关文献"},{"id":"名词译注","depth":2,"text":"名词译注"},{"id":"阅读更多","depth":2,"text":"阅读更多"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:7.gists:neuroscience.md","_source":"content","_file":"7.gists/neuroscience.md","_extension":"md"}